Marcus Says Inflation Forecasting Difficult in Current Climate

-- B y   M i k e   C o h e n
-- 
2011-10-12T09:42:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/marcus-says-inflation-forecasting-difficult-in-current-climate.html
South African Reserve Bank Governor
Gill Marcus said the current economic environment makes
inflation forecasting difficult.  The central bank is “not wedded” to the outcome of its
“suite” of inflation models, Marcus told lawmakers in  Cape
Town  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mike Cohen in Cape Town at 
 mcohen21@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
